WHAT IS PIU OVERCLOCK?

PIU OVERCLOCK is my first personal pack, which I made public a year after the beginning of its creation, the songs in this pack are based on my musical tastes and some are from other games or suggestions from my friends and players.
At first I didn't want to make this pack public and keep it private, since I just wanted to do a few charts. But seeing that my channel already had 87 songs, I simply decided to share it with the public. I'm glad it's been well received in the community.
If you want to try this pack, the download link, all the information, changelog and related videos are below.

INSTALLATION STEPS

COMPATIBILITY: This pack is ONLY compatible with PumpSanity, download this system here.
The way to install this pack is different from the old method of "Extract and move", this is due to take advantage of the features that PumpSanity offers, which you will notice during the explanation.

In the Google Drive folder you will find the following files:

  • OVERCLOCK Drive Folder/
    • SongPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK_Core.zip
    • UserPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK.spx
      • OVERCLOCK GLITCH.spx
      • OVERCLOCK_Bonus.zip
      • OVERCLOCK_BGA_1.0-2.1.zip
      • OVERCLOCK_GenericBGA.zip
    • OVERCLOCK_Info.txt

Download the drive folder as it is and then extract the drive-zipped folder into the PumpSanity root.
Anyways, here I explain what each file is for and its location.


"OVERCLOCK_Core.zip" - OBLIGATORY DOWNLOAD -
This ZIP file contains the multimedia files necessary for the pack to work.
Inside this zip you will find a copy of this page for offline reading.
This file must be in the specified path:

  • PumpSanity Root/
    • SongPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK_Core.zip


"OVERCLOCK.spx" and "OVERCLOCK GLITCH.spx" - OBLIGATORY DOWNLOAD -
Encrypted files, contains the charts and files necessary for the pack to work.
This files must be in the specified path:

  • PumpSanity Root/
    • UserPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK.spx
      • OVERCLOCK GLITCH.spx


"OVERCLOCK_Bonus.zip" - OPTIONAL -
Bonus files like Avatars, USBSkins and NoteSkins.
This files must be in the specified path:

  • PumpSanity Root/
    • UserPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK_Bonus.zip


"OVERCLOCK_BGA_1.0-2.1.zip" and "OVERCLOCK_GenericBGA.zip" - OPTIONAL -
ZIPs containing the BGAs of the songs.
This files must be in the specified path:

  • PumpSanity Root/
    • UserPackages/
      • OVERCLOCK_BGA_1.0-2.1.zip
      • OVERCLOCK_GenericBGA.zip

Or extract these zips in the PumpSanity root, the folders should look like this:

  • PumpSanity Root/
    • SongMovies/
      • OVERCLOCK_BGA/
        • ** BGA Files **


"OVERCLOCK_Info.txt" - NOT NECCESARY -
Contains quick information, such as the version of the pack and the release date.


This explanation may make installing the pack seem complicated, but it really isn't, the process doesn't take more than 1 minute.
If there are any errors, it is probably a layer 8 error.
WARNING: Don't rename the files, doing this will break the channel and it will be impossible to play it.

UPDATING OVERCLOCK

OVERCLOCK 2.1 ONWARDS: To update the pack, just download the required files again and replace the previous ones by following the installation process.

OVERCLOCK 2.0.1 AND PREVIOUS: If you already had a previous version of OVERCLOCK it is recommended to delete it, upgrading OVERCLOCK 2.0.1 to 2.1 is not supported due to massive order and game engine changes.

WHAT ABOUT STEPF2?: A "Portable" version will be released soon for any StepMania 5 and FiveSteps.
